Buyer Flow

1. Users Sign In or Go to Buyer Home Page directly
2. Select Products & add to cart.
3. Cart list Updated & Count of Cart Badge Increases.
3. Before checkout buyer should login with credentials / register self.
4. Cofirm Order before Payment.
5. Select Delivery type.
6. Proceed to payment & complete payment.
7. Receive PopUp of Order Details.


Seller Flow

1. Login with credentials / Request Admin to Register Seller.
2. Watch Orders for their respective store.
3. Watch stock for respective store.
4. 




Admin Flow

1. Login with Credentials
2. Watch all stores stock.
3. Get notofication for less stock
4. Order stock Manually by choosing previous Vendors
5. Create Seller
6. Product & Stock CRUD operations.
